{
  "stem": "25598.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like in Romania, you do what the five-year economic plan dictates, and that's what it dictated then.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I did so well that I remained as a teacher at-- at this institute.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And then I-- I worked at a newspaper in Romania and this teaching position.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was very involved with academic life and with academia and with theater and with opera, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] until I got that depression and I decided to leave with my parents.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I was fired from everywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also, applying to leave Romania was a very risky thing, because there was no rhyme-- we thought there was no rhyme or reason to who gets the visas-- the exit visas-- and who doesn't.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I later found out that there was some rhyme and reason.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But from the outside, it appeared like there wasn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when you applied, you didn't know if it's going to last a year, or if you're going to rot there for 20 years, or if you're going to rot there forever as an enemy of the country.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So eventually, I-- after I applied, I got some--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't find the job, because in your identity card, line number four said what your profession was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if they look at your profession and you are an assistant at the university, and you apply for a job as a cashier in a store or-- or in a bus, they know that there's some political issue involved here, so they're not hiring you.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So eventually I ended up working at the garbage-- at cleaning streets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sweeping streets, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] which was-- actually, turned out to be not too bad, once I got used to sweeping the streets, because I was very alert.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
